#: instructor-training/_extras/guide.md:26
msgid "-  Contact your co-Trainer(s) and decide who will teach what.  "
msgstr ""

# unordered list
#: instructor-training/_extras/guide.md:27
msgid ""
"-  Create an event Etherpad (using the [Etherpad template][etherpad-"
